{"id": "872075", "revid": "32911304", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=872075", "title": "The Bleeding Temple", "text": "The Bleeding Temple is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Imperial%20City%29\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; in .\nBackground.\n\"The minions of Molag Bal are rounding up the Imperial City's clergy and mercilessly torturing them. The Drake of Blades has asked for my help in rescuing one of these prisoners---a priest named Egnatius.\"\nWalkthrough.\nWhen you enter the &lt;a href=\"Temple%20District%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Temple District&lt;/a&gt; from the sewers, you will find the Drake of Blades there. Talk to her and she will tell you that she lost someone here, a priest called &lt;a href=\"Father%20Egnatius\"&gt;Father Egnatius&lt;/a&gt;. The enemy has kidnapped him and are constantly moving him about to avoid him being freed. the Drake will tell you that the daedra are torturing priests in the shrines here in the district; she hopes you will find Egnatius among them.\nSplit up and free the priests. Your targets are the shrines of Julianos in the northeast, Mara in the northwest and Dibella in the southwest. The last priest you rescue will tell you that Father Egnatius was dragged to the &lt;a href=\"Temple%20of%20the%20One\"&gt;Temple of the One&lt;/a&gt;. Bring this information to the Drake of Blades; you can find her in the Temple Rectory in the far southeast of the district. She will tell you to go into the temple and free Egnatius while she creates a distraction. \nHead to the temple in the middle of the district. You will find the daedra slaying priests there in an attempt to get Father Egnatius to tell them what he knows. Slay the daedra and a monster named &lt;a href=\"Uzuruz\"&gt;Uzuruz&lt;/a&gt; will appear. Once you have slain that beast, free Father Egnatius and he will tell you to head to the southwest of town. There, a well entrance will lead you to the Temple Hideout. Speak with the father inside and he will tell you about a scroll he found just before the invasion that probably holds relevant secrets. Unfortunately, he no longer possesses the scroll though. Bring this information to the Drake of Blades in the sewers to finish the quest. "}
