{"id": "1053837", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1053837", "title": "The Blue God", "text": "The Blue God is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Blades%29\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; available in . It revolves around stealing a blue statue of Malacath from the Iron Skull Clan of goblins, and planting the banner of the White Ghost tribe to weaken their alliance. The recommended player character level is the player character's level. Two secrets can be found during this quest.\nBackground.\n\"The goblin alliance still holds, so I must steal the sacred idol of Malacath known as the Blue God from the Iron Skull tribe, then plant evidence that incriminates the White Ghost tribe.\"\nObjectives.\nStatus: 0 of 8"}
