{"id": "21973", "revid": "32911304", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=21973", "title": "Hydnum Azure", "text": "Hydnum Azure grows on rocks all over the &lt;a href=\"Mania\"&gt;Mania&lt;/a&gt; side of the &lt;a href=\"Shivering%20Isles\"&gt;Shivering Isles&lt;/a&gt;. They may also be found on the island with the &lt;a href=\"Strange%20Door\"&gt;Strange Door&lt;/a&gt;. They only grow from the sides of objects like boulders, buildings, or large roots. The plant is large enough that it can be used as a platform to scale the sheer edifices it tends to grow on. The residents of Mania consume the plant's spores as part of their regular diets.\nQuests.\n&lt;a href=\"Taxonomy%20of%20Obsession\"&gt;Taxonomy of Obsession&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Mirili%20Ulven\"&gt;Mirili Ulven&lt;/a&gt; is creating a taxonomic catalog for everything in the &lt;a href=\"Shivering%20Isles\"&gt;Shivering Isles&lt;/a&gt;. Hydnum Azure is one of the ingredients the &lt;a href=\"Hero%20of%20Kvatch\"&gt;Hero&lt;/a&gt; needs to bring her."}
