{"id": "1041832", "revid": "32911304", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1041832", "title": "Ice Spike (Blades)", "text": "Ice Spike is a &lt;a href=\"Spells%20%28Blades%29\"&gt;spell&lt;/a&gt; in .\nUsage.\nThe ability of Ice Spike to stagger an opponent not resistant to ice means that a wight or a skeleton can be brought down more easily than goblins, which are susceptible to ice (as they have more effective counters at higher levels).\nThus, whenever fighting high-level wights and skeletons, if the Fugitive uses ice spike alongside the appropriate counter damage type (physical and elemental), makes use of blocks, dodges occasionally to avoid enemy damage, they are likely to win the fight relatively easily. This also works on goblins if countering their counters is learned."}
