{"id": "70113", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=70113", "title": "Ice Wolf Pelt", "text": "Ice Wolf Pelt is a &lt;a href=\"Miscellaneous%20Items%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;miscellaneous item&lt;/a&gt; dropped by the common &lt;a href=\"Ice%20Wolf%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;ice wolves&lt;/a&gt; found in the snowy, mountainous parts of &lt;a href=\"Skyrim\"&gt;Skyrim&lt;/a&gt;.\nUses.\nThey are used to craft &lt;a href=\"Leather%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;leather&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Conjure%20Frost%20Atronach\"&gt;Conjure Frost Atronach&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Tomes%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;Spell Tomes&lt;/a&gt;. One pelt yields one piece of leather, which can then be turned into four &lt;a href=\"Leather%20Strips\"&gt;Leather Strips&lt;/a&gt;, when stripped at a &lt;a href=\"Tanning%20Rack\"&gt;Tanning Rack&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;a href=\"Blacksmiths%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;Blacksmiths&lt;/a&gt; are willing to buy them."}
