{"id": "902975", "revid": "32911304", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=902975", "title": "Icewind Peaks", "text": "Icewind Peaks is a &lt;a href=\"subzone\"&gt;subzone&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Eastmarch%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Eastmarch&lt;/a&gt; in . It is the southeastern of the three subzones in Eastmarch, reaching from &lt;a href=\"Cragwallow\"&gt;Cragwallow&lt;/a&gt; in the north to &lt;a href=\"Direfrost%20Keep\"&gt;Direfrost Keep&lt;/a&gt; in the south. Icewind Peaks is the final subzone of Eastmarch the &lt;a href=\"Vestige\"&gt;Vestige&lt;/a&gt; is likely to visit after &lt;a href=\"Giant%27s%20Run\"&gt;Giant's Run&lt;/a&gt; which borders it to the north and &lt;a href=\"Frostwater%20Tundra\"&gt;Frostwater Tundra&lt;/a&gt; which borders it to the west.\nLocations.\n &lt;a href=\"Jorunn%27s%20Stand%20Wayshrine\"&gt;Jorunn's Stand Wayshrine&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Logging%20Camp%20Wayshrine\"&gt;Logging Camp Wayshrine&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Skuldafn%20Wayshrine\"&gt;Skuldafn Wayshrine&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Direfrost%20Keep\"&gt;Direfrost Keep&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Stormcrag%20Crypt\"&gt;Stormcrag Crypt&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"The%20Bastard%27s%20Tomb%20%28Location%29\"&gt;The Bastar's Tomb&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Cragwallow\"&gt;Cragwallow&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Jorunn%27s%20Stand\"&gt;Jorunn's Stand&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Mzulft%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Mzulft&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Skuldafn%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Skuldafn&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Thulvald%27s%20Logging%20Camp\"&gt;Thulvald's Logging Camp&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Hammerhome\"&gt;Hammerhome&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"The%20Ritual%20%28Online%29\"&gt;The Ritual&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Icewind%20Peaks%20Dolmen\"&gt;Icewind Peaks Dolmen&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Ammabani%27s%20Pride\"&gt;Ammabani's Pride&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Swiftblade%27s%20Camp\"&gt;Swiftblade's Camp&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Bitterblade%27s%20Camp\"&gt;Bitterblade's Camp&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Cragwallow%20Cave\"&gt;Cragwallow Cave&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Border%20Crossings%20%28Online%29%23Eastmarch\"&gt;Border Crossing&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Hfirorg%20Farm\"&gt;Hfirorg Farm&lt;/a&gt;"}
