{"id": "927673", "revid": "32911304", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=927673", "title": "Icy Shore", "text": "Icy Shore, also known as Eastern Wrothgar, is a &lt;a href=\"subzone\"&gt;subzone&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Wrothgar%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Wrothgar&lt;/a&gt; in . It is the eastern of the three subzones of Wrothgar, reaching from &lt;a href=\"Merchant%27s%20Gate\"&gt;Merchant's Gate&lt;/a&gt; in the south to &lt;a href=\"Icy%20Shore%20Wayshrine\"&gt;Icy Shore Wayshrine&lt;/a&gt; in the north and stretching to the region's eastern border and northeast coast. It is bordered to the west by the &lt;a href=\"Morkul%20Plain\"&gt;Morkul Plain&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Frostbreak%20Ridge\"&gt;Frostbreak Ridge&lt;/a&gt; is further west. Icy Shore is characterized by its snowy mountains and &lt;a href=\"Dwemer%20Ruins%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Dwemer ruins&lt;/a&gt; scattered throughout. The &lt;a href=\"Orsimer%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Orsimer&lt;/a&gt; city of &lt;a href=\"Orsinium%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Orsinium&lt;/a&gt; is located at the base of the mountain in the subzone's south.\nLocations.\n &lt;a href=\"Icy%20Shore%20Wayshrine\"&gt;Icy Shore Wayshrine&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Merchant%27s%20Gate%20Wayshrine\"&gt;Merchant's Gate Wayshrine&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Orsinium%20Wayshrine\"&gt;Orsinium Wayshrine&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Shatul%20Wayshrine\"&gt;Shatul Wayshrine&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Two%20Rivers%20Wayshrine\"&gt;Two Rivers Wayshrine&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Coldperch%20Cavern\"&gt;Coldperch Cavern&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Icereach\"&gt;Icereach&lt;/a&gt; \n &lt;a href=\"Maelstrom%20Arena%20%28Location%29\"&gt;Maelstrom Arena&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Rkindaleft\"&gt;Rkindaleft&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Zthenganaz\"&gt;Zthenganaz&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Bonerock%20Cavern\"&gt;Bonerock Cavern&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Fharun%20Stronghold\"&gt;Fharun Stronghold&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Frozen%20Fleet\"&gt;Frozen Fleet&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Merchant%27s%20Gate\"&gt;Merchant's Gate&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Orsinium%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Orsinium&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Shatul%20Range\"&gt;Shatul Range&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Sorrow\"&gt;Sorrow&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Malacath%20Statue\"&gt;Malacath Statue&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Morkuldin%20Forge\"&gt;Morkuldin Forge&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"King-Chief%27s%20Throne\"&gt;King-Chief's Throne&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Nyzchaleft%20Falls\"&gt;Nyzchaleft Falls&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"The%20Mad%20Ogre%27s%20Altar\"&gt;The Mad Ogre's Altar&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Forlorn%20Watchtower\"&gt;Forlorn Watchtower&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Jehanna%20Docks\"&gt;Jehanna Docks&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Torug%27s%20Arch\"&gt;Torug's Arch&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Pariah%27s%20Pinnacle\"&gt;Pariah's Pinnacle&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Bloody%20Knoll\"&gt;Bloody Knoll&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Coldwind%27s%20Den\"&gt;Coldwind's Den&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Morkul%20Descent\"&gt;Morkul Descent&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Orzorga%27s%20Kitchen\"&gt;Orzorga's Kitchen&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Sanctuary%20of%20Malacath\"&gt;Sanctuary of Malacath&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Signal%20Tower\"&gt;Signal Tower&lt;/a&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"Smuggler%27s%20Bolt\"&gt;Smuggler's Bolt&lt;/a&gt;"}
