: \"\"[to son] Do you believe this old hag? [to Fralia] \"Holding him\"? Why, I've got him in my cellar. He's my prisoner. Face it, cow! Your stupid son is dead! He died a Stormcloak traitor. And you...you best keep your mouth shut before you suffer the same.\"\"\nIdolaf: \"Come on, father. There's nothing more to be said here.\""}
