{"id": "620555", "revid": "17401442", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=620555", "title": "If the Dead Could Talk", "text": "If the Dead Could Talk is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Online%29\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; available in . It takes place near &lt;a href=\"Root%20Sunder%20Ruins\"&gt;Root Sunder Ruins&lt;/a&gt;, northwest of &lt;a href=\"Haven%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Haven&lt;/a&gt;. Tandare asks the &lt;a href=\"Vestige\"&gt;Vestige&lt;/a&gt; to find the journals of a research crew that died in the ruins.\nBackground.\n\"A research team from Elden Root has rediscovered the ancient city of Root Sunder. Unfortuanely they've also been mauled by wild animals. Tandare, the last survivor of the research team, needs the journals of her dead comrades.\"\nWalkthrough.\nOutside of the &lt;a href=\"Root%20Sunder%20Ruins\"&gt;Root Sunder Ruins&lt;/a&gt;, you will meet an &lt;a href=\"Altmer%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Altmer&lt;/a&gt; named Tandare. She will explain that she is part of a research team investigating the ruins of the ancient Altmer city of Root Sunder, but that the ruins were overrun by wild animals while she was out getting supplies. She will ask you to head in and retrieve the journals of her colleagues so that the expedition was not a complete waste. \nHead inside. You will immediately be greeted by a ghost called &lt;a href=\"Sirdor\"&gt;Sirdor&lt;/a&gt; who will give you the quest \"&lt;a href=\"Forgotten%20Soul\"&gt;Forgotten Soul&lt;/a&gt;.\" That quest takes place in the same area as this one, so it can be efficient to do both simultaneously. Head on towards the first room and you will find \"&lt;a href=\"Uryaamo%27s%20Journal\"&gt;Uryaamo's Journal&lt;/a&gt;\" to the north of the water. Head through the hallway to the west and you will find the room that contains \"&lt;a href=\"Ruurifin%27s%20Journal%2C%20Entry%201\"&gt;Ruurifin's Journal, Entry 1&lt;/a&gt;\" as well as a skyshard. Finally, head through the hallway east of the central room until you reach a room with a glowing crystal on an island. This room contains the remains of &lt;a href=\"Researcher%20Tancano\"&gt;Researcher Tancano&lt;/a&gt;, as well as \"&lt;a href=\"Tancano%20the%20Elder%27s%20Journal\"&gt;his journal&lt;/a&gt;\". \nOnce you have all three journals, head outside and give them to Tandare to complete the quest."}
