{"id": "1067161", "revid": "26459635", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1067161", "title": "Hircine's Gift", "text": "Hircine's Gift is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Online%29\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; available in . It gives the &lt;a href=\"Lycanthropy%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Werewolf&lt;/a&gt; skill line upon completion.\nBackground.\n\"A strange woman met me at the gates to the city. She may be a werewolf. She told me I am on my way to becoming one as well.\"\nWalkthrough.\n&lt;a href=\"Sanies%20Lupinus\"&gt;Sanies Lupinus&lt;/a&gt; must be contracted to start this quest. This can be from either being bitten by another player, or from fighting a wild werewolf (can sometimes be found in select locations at night in &lt;a href=\"Bangkorai\"&gt;Bangkorai&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Reaper%27s%20March\"&gt;Reaper's March&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"The%20Rift%20%28Online%29\"&gt;The Rift&lt;/a&gt;).\nNext, look for Thoreki (found in either &lt;a href=\"Evermore%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Evermore&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Rawl%27kha%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Rawl'kha&lt;/a&gt;, or &lt;a href=\"Riften%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Riften&lt;/a&gt;, depending on your alliance). She sends the &lt;a href=\"Vestige\"&gt;Vestige&lt;/a&gt; to look for the packmaster &lt;a href=\"Songamdir\"&gt;Songamdir&lt;/a&gt;, found in &lt;a href=\"Viridian%20Woods\"&gt;Viridian Woods&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Fort%20Sphinxmoth%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Fort Sphinxmoth&lt;/a&gt;, or &lt;a href=\"Fort%20Greenwall%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Fort Greenwall&lt;/a&gt;. He will open a portal to &lt;a href=\"Hircine%27s%20Hunting%20Grounds%20%28Hircine%27s%20Gift%29\"&gt;Hircine's Hunting Grounds&lt;/a&gt;.\nHead through the portal and into Hircine's realm. There, Songamdir will tell you to use the altar and speak to Hircine himself. Hircine will tell you that in order to be accepted into the pack, you must hunt down a prey and then howl to your brothers and sisters. If they accept you, you will feast together and you will be one of the pack. After Hircine is done talking, you will transform into your wolf form. You can talk to Songamdir again, but he will not tell you anything meaningful. \nHead out and explore the realm. You will find many &lt;a href=\"Harpy%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Harpies&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Senche-Tiger%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Senche-Tigers&lt;/a&gt; around, but these will not be sufficient. Your prey should be the &lt;a href=\"Troll%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Troll&lt;/a&gt; found all the way on in the south of this plane. Once you have killed it, howl to your pack, and they will come to feed on it. Feast with them, and Hircine will tell you to come back to his shrine so that he may bestow true power onto you. \nHead back and talk to Hircine's statue again to finish the quest and unlock the Werewolf skill tree. You will be transformed back after this."}
