{"id": "211123", "revid": "39973906", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=211123", "title": "Hiring Guards", "text": "Hiring Guards is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Bloodmoon%29\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; in .\nWalkthrough.\nUpon completing \"&lt;a href=\"Razing%20the%20Forest\"&gt;Razing the Forest&lt;/a&gt;,\" Falco or Carnius will want you to ask the townsfolk of Raven Rock whether they'd be willing to act as guards for the colony.\nHead over to Raven Rock and ask the townsfolk whether they are willing to act as guards. Only three will accept: &lt;a href=\"Afer%20Flaccus\"&gt;Afer Flaccus&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Gratian%20Caerellius%20%28Bloodmoon%29\"&gt;Gratian Caerellus&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Garnas%20Uvalen\"&gt;Garnas Uvalen&lt;/a&gt;. Afer can be found in the bar, Garnas will be in the eastern part of town (where you killed the spriggans), and Gratian can be found in the mine.\nOnce you have recruited one or more guards, return to your questgiver for your reward. The size of your reward will depend on how many guards you have recruited."}
