{"id": "68365", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=68365", "title": "Histskin", "text": "Histskin is a &lt;a href=\"Abilities%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;racial ability&lt;/a&gt; granted to &lt;a href=\"Argonians%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;Argonians&lt;/a&gt; in . It is a greater power that improves &lt;a href=\"Health%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;health&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Restore%20Health%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;restoration&lt;/a&gt; 10x for 60 seconds. As a visual effect, it causes the caster's frame to glow with a luminous golden light. When an Argonian is injured or near death they can call to &lt;a href=\"the%20Hist\"&gt;the Hist&lt;/a&gt; to heal them of any ailments or injuries. Many Argonians assume that the Hist themselves heal them through magic, and as such they revere the Hist even more."}
