{"id": "145840", "revid": "26208079", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=145840", "title": "Hlaalu Guard", "text": "Hlaalu Guards are the appointed &lt;a href=\"Guards%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;guards&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"House%20Hlaalu%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;House Hlaalu&lt;/a&gt;. Their responsibility is to guard the cities of &lt;a href=\"House%20Hlaalu%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;House Hlaalu&lt;/a&gt;. As defined in the &lt;a href=\"Treaty%20of%20the%20Armistice\"&gt;Treaty of the Armistice&lt;/a&gt;, it is them, rather than the &lt;a href=\"Imperial%20Legion%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Imperial Legion&lt;/a&gt;, that secures the city of &lt;a href=\"Balmora%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Balmora&lt;/a&gt;. They will not be aggressive normally, unless they see the &lt;a href=\"Nerevarine\"&gt;Nerevarine&lt;/a&gt; committing a &lt;a href=\"Crime%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;crime&lt;/a&gt;, in which case they will start pursuit."}
