{"id": "1008728", "revid": "17401442", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1008728", "title": "Hlaalu Schemes", "text": "Hlaalu Schemes is one of the five purchasable &lt;a href=\"deck\"&gt;deck&lt;/a&gt;s in added with the expansion. It costs (USD/EUR $/\u20ac7.99) or 1,000 and is a &lt;a href=\"Strength%20%28Legends%29\"&gt;strength&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Willpower%20%28Legends%29\"&gt;willpower&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Agility%20%28Legends%29\"&gt;agility&lt;/a&gt; deck that represents &lt;a href=\"House%20Hlaalu\"&gt;House Hlaalu&lt;/a&gt;.\nStrategy.\nThis deck revolves around the &lt;a href=\"Plot\"&gt;Plot&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"keyword\"&gt;keyword&lt;/a&gt; which requires the summoner to play one or more cards before the Plot effect is triggered. Therefore, Hlaalu Schemes does not have a lot of &lt;a href=\"Magicka%20%28Legends%29\"&gt;Magicka&lt;/a&gt;-expensive cards, and contains cards that generate other cards. Some &lt;a href=\"Creatures%20%28Legends%29\"&gt;creatures&lt;/a&gt; also keep the summoner's hand full, discount Magicka costs or give the summoner more Magicka for a turn to help trigger Plot abilities. This deck does not have any powerful creatures for later turns and so benefits from semi-aggressive gameplay."}
