{"id": "45390", "revid": "44356307", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=45390", "title": "Hlaren Ramoran", "text": "Hlaren Ramoran is a &lt;a href=\"Dunmer%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Dunmer&lt;/a&gt; Knight in &lt;a href=\"Morrowind\"&gt;Morrowind&lt;/a&gt; who serves as a &lt;a href=\"Councilor\"&gt;Councilor&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=\"House%20Redoran\"&gt;House Redoran&lt;/a&gt; and the lord\u00a0of Gnisis.\nBackground.\nRamoran may be located in his Private Quarters in his manor in &lt;a href=\"Ald%27ruhn%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Ald'ruhn&lt;/a&gt;. When the &lt;a href=\"Nerevarine\"&gt;Nerevarine&lt;/a&gt; comes to him seeking his support, he first asks the Nerevarine to collect some taxes from Hetman Abelmawia in Gnisis.\nAfterwards, he will ask the Nerevarine to find an old acquaintance of his named &lt;a href=\"Nalvilie%20Saren%20%28Character%29\"&gt;Nalvilie Saren&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0whom he still holds feelings for. After Nalvilie rejects him, he will attempt to track her down himself. Or, the Nerevarine can convince him to forget the past and reveal to him that his loyal servant, &lt;a href=\"Nalvyna%20Sarinith\"&gt;Nalvyna Sarinith&lt;/a&gt;, cares for him very deeply.\nAccording to the House Redoran book, \"&lt;a href=\"Red%20Book%20of%203E%20426\"&gt;Red Book of 3E 426&lt;/a&gt;\", Ramoran is the \"Lord of &lt;a href=\"West%20Gash%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;West Gash&lt;/a&gt;,\" and resides in \"Ramoran Manor.\" This region includes the town of &lt;a href=\"Gnisis%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Gnisis&lt;/a&gt;. Several official documents, including \"&lt;a href=\"Widow%20Vabdas%27%20Land%20Deed\"&gt;Widow Vabdas' Land Deed&lt;/a&gt;\", list him as the ruler of Gnisis."}
{"id": "136532", "revid": "44356307", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=136532", "title": "Hlaren Residence", "text": ", \"&lt;a href=\"Vivec%2C%20Telvanni%20Canton\"&gt;Telvanni Canton&lt;/a&gt;\"\nHlaren Residence is a house found in .\nDescription.\nThe residence is located on the &lt;a href=\"Telvanni%20Plaza\"&gt;plaza&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=\"Vivec%2C%20Telvanni%20Canton\"&gt;Telvanni Canton&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Vivec%20City%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Vivec City&lt;/a&gt;. It is a small house, where &lt;a href=\"Fendel%20Hlaren\"&gt;Fendel Hlaren&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Kalorter%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Kalorter&lt;/a&gt; can be found. There is a library containing &lt;a href=\"Books%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;books&lt;/a&gt;, a large table and many ingredients stashed in baskets in the corner of the room. The other section has two beds and a cupboard."}
