s. Beside a bedroll some alcoholic beverages and &lt;a href=\"Potions%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;potions&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Ingredients%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;food&lt;/a&gt; and a vast collection of &lt;a href=\"Weapons%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;weapons&lt;/a&gt; can be found.\nDialogue.\n\"What do you want?\""}
