{"id": "1091653", "revid": "32911304", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1091653", "title": "Ember (Character)", "text": "Ember is a &lt;a href=\"Khajiit%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Khajiit&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Companions%20%28Online%29\"&gt;companion&lt;/a&gt; in .\nBackground.\nA talented Mage and former street kid, Ember is a chaotic, earnest, notorious troublemaker. In short, she is a certified disaster. Call this companion to your side for a bit of chaos and help her fuel her endless curiosity for mystic knowledge. \nBefore she became a magical prodigy, she was a street kid, living in &lt;a href=\"Skywatch\"&gt;Skywatch&lt;/a&gt;. She ran with a crew of three other kids, &lt;a href=\"Jhaka\"&gt;Jhaka&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Silverslip\"&gt;Silverslip&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Song\"&gt;Song&lt;/a&gt;, taking care of organizing food for the group. One day, her friends disappeared, leaving nothing but traces of struggle behind. She left Skywatch shortly afterwards, becoming a vagrant, but never forgetting her friends. She was worried someone was targeting her as the sole survivor of the group, although she kept an ear to the ground, trying to find leads that would allow her to figure out what happened to her friends. \nEmber is a nickname she uses pretty much exclusively to refer to herself. It stems from her fiery eyes, who someone once described as \"embers in a flame.\" She still thinks flames are prettier.\n&lt;a href=\"Companions%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Companion&lt;/a&gt;.\nEmber becomes available as a companion after completing \"Tower Full of Trouble\" at &lt;a href=\"Tor%20Draioch\"&gt;Tor Draioch&lt;/a&gt;. She is essentially a rogue-type companion, who appreciates thievery, pickpocketing, and work for the mages guild. She loves animals, with the notable exception of canines. \nRapport breakdown:"}
