{"id": "902352", "revid": "24931587", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=902352", "title": "Enchanter Certification", "text": "Enchanter Certification is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Online%29\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; available in . The &lt;a href=\"Vestige\"&gt;Vestige&lt;/a&gt; learns the basics of enchanting from &lt;a href=\"Danel%20Telleno\"&gt;Danel Telleno&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=\"Mages%20Guild%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Mages Guild&lt;/a&gt;. Completing this quest unlocks the ability to pick up and fulfill daily &lt;a href=\"Enchanter%20Writ\"&gt;Enchanter Writ&lt;/a&gt;s from the Consumables Crafting Writs board in any large city.\nBackground.\n\"If I can prove I know my way around an enchanting table, Danel Telleno will certify me as an enchanter.\"\nWalkthrough.\nThis quest can be initiated by speaking to &lt;a href=\"Danel%20Telleno\"&gt;Danel Telleno&lt;/a&gt;, who can be found at the Mages Guild in any alliance's starting city (&lt;a href=\"Daggerfall%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Daggerfall&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Davon%27s%20Watch%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Davon's Watch&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Vulkhel%20Guard%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Vulkhel Guard&lt;/a&gt;). Alternatively, if you have just completed the &lt;a href=\"Alchemist%20Certification\"&gt;Alchemist&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Provisioner%20Certification\"&gt;Provisioner Certification&lt;/a&gt;, Danel Telleno can be found nearby. \nDanel Telleno explains that enchanters harness runes found in the wilds of Tamriel and transform them into certain glyphs depending on the rune. Potency, Essence, and Aspect Runes are combined to create a glyph which can in turn add enchantments to items. He tells you to acquire three runes, one each of Jora, Oko, and Ta, and mentions a convenient cache outside of town. If you already have the required runes, it is still useful to take advantage of the highlighted search area to gather more runes for later use. The contents of runestone nodes are random, so it may be necessary to search other locations. Jora runes can also be purchased from an Enchanter's shop. \nAfter obtaining the required runes, return to Danel Telleno, who has moved to the city's Enchanting Table. He instructs you to craft a glyph from the Jora, Oko, and Ta runes. Show the completed Trifling Glyph of Health to Danel Telleno, who allows you to keep it and certifies you to fulfill &lt;a href=\"Enchanter%20Writ\"&gt;Enchanter Writ&lt;/a&gt;s. "}
