{"id": "86686", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=86686", "title": "Rout", "text": "Rout is an Expert-level &lt;a href=\"Illusion%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;Illusion&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Spells%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;spell&lt;/a&gt; in .\nEffects.\nRout causes a creature or character to flee from the area for 30 seconds. This spell will work on creatures and characters up to level 20 (or more when &lt;a href=\"dual-cast\"&gt;dual-cast&lt;/a&gt;).\nPerks.\nWhen the Illusion perks &lt;a href=\"Aspect%20of%20Terror%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;Aspect of Terror&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Kindred%20Mage\"&gt;Kindred Mage&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Animage\"&gt;Animage&lt;/a&gt; have been activated, this spell causes characters and creatures up to level 30 to flee from the area for 30 seconds."}
{"id": "93528", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=93528", "title": "Rovone Arvel", "text": "Rovone Arvel is a &lt;a href=\"Dunmer%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Dunmer&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Noble%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Noble&lt;/a&gt; and member of &lt;a href=\"House%20Hlaalu%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;House Hlaalu&lt;/a&gt; who resides on the &lt;a href=\"Arvel%20Plantation\"&gt;Arvel Plantation&lt;/a&gt;.\nInteractions.\n&lt;a href=\"Sealed%20Orders%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Sealed Orders&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Crassius%20Curio\"&gt;Crassius Curio&lt;/a&gt; has requested that the &lt;a href=\"Nerevarine\"&gt;Nerevarine&lt;/a&gt; speak with &lt;a href=\"Odral%20Helvi\"&gt;Odral Helvi&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Caldera%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Caldera&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Erroneous%20Documents\"&gt;Erroneous Documents&lt;/a&gt;.\nOdral Helvi wants to replace a scroll in the Hlaalu Records in &lt;a href=\"Vivec%20City%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Vivec City&lt;/a&gt;. The Records are part of the treasury, which is in the top level of the Hlaalu Waistworks on the north side.\n&lt;a href=\"Rent%20and%20Taxes\"&gt;Rent and Taxes&lt;/a&gt;.\nOdral Helvi has requested to collect 50 gold in rent and taxes from &lt;a href=\"Manat%20Varnan-Adda\"&gt;Manat Varnan-Adda&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Llovyn%20Andus\"&gt;Llovyn Andus&lt;/a&gt;. If they refuse to pay the rent, then killing them is an appropriate course of action."}
